i asked molli what to put in my journal so this what im putting...
PuFfMaMa03MD: that we are a bunch of losers but its ok cuz we can pull it off cuz we're cool like that
PuFfMaMa03MD: ;-)
I have too many games this week! I have 3 volleyball games and 2 football games! Well maybe we'll win against crestview if I change into my wind-suit during the 3rd quarter instead of Half-Time!!>:o That would have been a lot funnier if that had happened to someone besides me!!!!Why do all the funny things that happen that involve me have to do with guys! Oh God I just remembered the gay little 5th grade boys incident! I best stop writing.

I don't really write much in this thing but oh well. I want someone to write a song about me! I'm listening to Sarah and if Sarah has a song named after her,I defiantly think someone should write one about me or at least after me!!!

I just got back from my dad's. Life in West Virginia was just swell. I'd come back once in a while to see my cousins on the weekend when my dad had off. Coming back here for me sucked,its soo depressing in Lisbon!:(Life hasn't been going my way necessarily. I'm not trying to sound like I'm a huge drama queen like I got dumped or got in a fight with a friend or whatever. There's been a lot of really sucky family issues mainly including me and it just sucks. It's kinda getting to the point where I'm not sure I can take all the stuff happening at school and life at home. God knows there will be lots of drama at school! Now I realize who are my real friends,the people that have time to hear all these wonderful things (It's depressing enough I'm writing in this!) Maddy and Molli I love you guys! I'm soo lucky I have friends like you! The kind that are losers like me!!:)haha good times! Well I best be going I gotta babysit tomorrow morning to earn some dough!
Fathers Day really sucks when you can't even see your dad!

nothin else to do at like 12 so wat better than write in here! My recitail is tomorrow and I'm really excited! I really want people to come to it because then I'll feel all akward after the show!:( Today I realized how nasty I've been to people in the past and I kinda feel really bad about it.I was really mean when i was like in a chatroom or whatever with JOHN! Of all people why would that fruit make me act all mean! I really do have issues!:) oh well.....I don't have anything else to say so I guess I'm done lol

I love summer and all but theres nothin to do but fry from the heat!So what better to do than type or write or whatever in this journal! Now that Ursies at camp I have nothing to do but go to volleyball camp and then come home and do nothing exciting! I dread saying this but i miss being busy all the time! It kept me from being bored at least! Next thing I know I'll start counting the days til school starts again! (*GASP!*) Well Molli is coming over tomorrow and I have vball camp so i guess thats some stuff to do.Maybe I'll jus watch tv and get fat on fudgesickles all day!...lol RIGHT JOHN!I have dress rehearsal one of these days and my recital is on saturday too! HOORAY MORE THINGS TO DO!
What do u put in here!? theres nothing on my mind to write about and im starting to think thats a bad thing!!! oh Well!

A bunch of other kiddies had this so i figured why not!? right now im very annoyed its hot in this darn house and bunch of ppl were in the room lookin over my shoulder! well i think this is a good start for a journal i suppose
